uit City 250|RCH]]\n| [[Diamond Hill Plywood 200|DAR]]\n| [[Carquest Auto Parts 300|CLT]]\n| [[StonebridgeRacing.com 200|DOV]]\n| [[Federated Auto Parts 300|NSH]]\n| [[Meijer 300|KEN]]\n| [[AT&T 250|MLW]]\n| [[Winn-Dixie 250|DAY]]\n| [[USG Durock 300|CHI]]\n| [[New England 200 (Nationwide)|NHA]]\n| [[Goody's 250|MAR]]\n| [[Busch Silver Celebration 250|GTY]]\n| [[Kroger 200 (Nationwide)|IRP]]\n| [[Zippo 200 at The Glen|GLN]]\n| style=\"background:#FFCFCF;\"| [[Carfax 250|MCH]]<br><small>DNQ</small>\n| [[Food City 250|BRI]]\n| [[Ameriquest 300|CAL]]\n| [[Emerson Radio 250|RCH]]\n| [[Dover 200 (fall race)|DOV]]\n| [[Yellow Transportation 300|KAN]]\n| [[Dollar General 300|CLT]]\n| colspan=4|\n! rowspan=2| 129th\n! rowspan=2| 67\n|-\n! [[Spraker Racing Enterprises]]\n! 63\n! [[Ford Motor Company|Ford]]\n| colspan=31|\n| style=\"background:#CFCFFF;\"| [[Sam's Town 250|MEM]]<br><small>32</small>\n| [[O'Reilly Challenge|TEX]]\n| [[Arizona.Travel 200|PHO]]\n| [[Ford 300 (Homestead-Miami)|HOM]]\n|-\n! [[2015 NASCAR Xfinity Series|2015]]\n! rowspan=5| [[King Autosport]]\n! rowspan=2| 92\n! rowspan=8| [[Chevrolet|Chevy]]\n| style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[Alert Today Florida 300|DAY]]<br><small>40</small>\n| [[Hisense 250|ATL]]\n| style=\"background:#FFCFCF;\"| [[Boyd Gaming 300|LVS]]<br><small>DNQ</small>\n| [[Axalta Faster. Tougher. Brighter. 200|PHO]]\n| [[Drive4Clots.com 300|CAL]]\n| [[O'Reilly Auto Parts 300|TEX]]\n| [[Drive to Stop Diabetes 300|BRI]]\n| [[ToyotaCare 250|RCH]]\n| [[Winn-Dixie 300|TAL]]\n| [[3M 250|IOW]]\n| [[Hisense 300|CLT]]\n| [[Buckle Up 200|DOV]]\n| [[Great Clips 250|MCH]]\n| [[Owens Corning AttiCat 300|CHI]]\n| style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[Subway Firecracker 250|DAY]]<br><small>40</small>\n| [[Kentucky 300|KEN]]\n| [[Sta-Green 200|NHA]]\n| [[Lilly Diabetes 250|IND]]\n| [[U.S. Cellular 250|IOW]]\n| [[Zippo 200 at The Glen|GLN]]\n| [[Nationwide Children's Hospital 200|MOH]]\n| [[Food City 300|BRI]]\n| [[Road America 180|ROA]]\n| [[VFW Sport Clips H